text: Pseudoechthistatus acutipennis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Chiang in 1981.BioLib.cz - Pseudoechthistatus acutipennis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Phrissomini Category:Beetles described in 1981
